{"tid":553304,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"由於父母既反面教材，我由細到大都好睇唔起d所謂追夢既人。","createTime":"2018-02-07T10:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T04:48:13.000Z","uid":24615,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f8a011fc4f4c65d814d92e812b9605adfb39e7","tid":553304,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"屋企人係熱愛追夢既人，所以我既童年係過住差唔多冇人理既生活，畢竟追夢既人係唔鍾意比柴米油鹽湊細路理屋企呢d野綁住。佢地兩個都好有個性，於是之後思想有分歧就離左婚，於是我更加冇人理。<br />\n<br />\n於是我由細到大都覺得果d所謂追夢永不放棄永不妥協既人 另一面就係不負責任 傷害身邊既人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但大大下，唔知係咪基因事，我自己都慢慢變左呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f839a5c29f159eadadbeb9eb98569248d619630a","tid":553304,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"追咩夢？"},{"pid":"5f95cf3f8a3e8d755f0587a971644802bfd77da4","tid":553304,"uid":104213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"當你慢慢向個目標前進個份開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3060011ff48c2ddba581e1a759caa0d8012e64","tid":553304,"uid":100809,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"你父母果d係叫任性 唔係叫追夢囉"},{"pid":"b1aac136924fdf3dd620b4b78ecd0686f445effa","tid":553304,"uid":60858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"你爸媽嗰啲叫無責任感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd206f7466acbc065daf64c5811eda76e4dd26d9","tid":553304,"uid":90929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"追夢冇問題  唔好生仔害下一代<br />\n<br />\n我都一直視父母為反面教材，發誓唔要做佢地，但逐漸發現自己處事（特別係情緒上）愈嚟愈似佢地，唉頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9e7b9c12ae9d2a5351f8f1fc7855230e78099d","tid":553304,